title: The Death of Paul Levi
view-if: year == 1930 and month >= 2
frequency: 1000
max-visits: 1
on-arrival: levi_dead = 1; n_advisors -= 1 if levi_advisor == 1; levi_advisor = 0; workers_sapd *= 0.75 if sapd_formed == 1 and sapd_consolidated != 1; workers_sapd *= 0.9 if sapd_consolidated == 1
tags: event

我党左翼领袖保罗·列维（Paul Levi）在一场不幸的事故中去世。他将被铭记。
